<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.5">
<l>cuṭalai yilcuṭu nīṟaṉa marntatōr</l>
<l>naṭalai tīrttava ṉainaṟai yūrkaṇṭeṉ</l>
<l>uṭalai yuḷpukun tuḷḷamu rukkiyuṇ</l>
<l>viṭalai yaicceṉṟu kāṇṭumey yattuḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen in Naṟaiyūr the one who ended the suffering</l>
<l>Placed  on the one covered in the hot ash of the cremation grounds,</l>
<l>We will go see in Meyyam the youth who rejoices,</l>
<l>Entering into my body where my heart was melted.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
